Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:02.78,Index II main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,How is the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:04.87,Index II main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,She has yet to regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.43,Index II main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Is could be heat stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.01,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Heat stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:10.83,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:11.73,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.29,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:18.20,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had gotten enough water and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.45,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I must be an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:23.75,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:24.94,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.13,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.83,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:33.06,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's still making that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.77,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:39.24,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best so everyone could enjoy themselves.{I tried my best so everyone could have fun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.19,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:00.03,Index II main,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:43.95,Index II main I,Red,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was lose my trump card, and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.85,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan has destroyed Oriana's Short Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.41,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling? Are you doing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.73,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.96,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there are no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.11,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.95,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then please use the Rihashijin Circle search spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.81,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've already prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.49,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You know what to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.87,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Don't belittle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.46,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how are things at your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.67,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can know, Oriana's counterspell was activated in the middle of an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.49,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.19,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,One student was injured, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.02,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to slip out in the resulting confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.76,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.85,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kamijou Touma go berserk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.36,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Since you understand, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:40.43,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act now, that student's sacrifice will have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.35,Index II main I,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:52.12,Index II main I,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why we resent our own inexperience?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.21,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is a twist I didn't expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:07.16,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed Oriana Thomson's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.59,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,She's near Futsuka Station in the Seventh District. {She's near Futsuka Station in the 7th District.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.18,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, she's at the Futsuka Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.76,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Futsuka Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:14.71,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,We've already passed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.87,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,She's heading north.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.26,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,The street splits in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.54,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,She's taken the one in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.53,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.59,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.92,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,A bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.34,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:59.08,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kami-yan, were there any other passengers besides Oriana on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.78,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,That's not important right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.55,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.47,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anyone! No passengers or the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.62,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.05,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.55,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's Number 5-1-4-4-5-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:22.37,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The rune that Stiyl placed back in the maintenance garage was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:37.96,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to try harder to get big sis heated up. {The physical flame can't get big sis heated up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.92,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.23,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,that was enough to make me panic. {That was enough to make me panic so I get wet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.30,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See this? {Wanna take a look?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.73,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My underwear is sopping wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.45,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,That spell you set up hurt an unrelated and innocent person. {That spell you set up hurt an unrelated person.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:58.64,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,To you, is there a difference in people who can and cannot wield magic?{Did it look like she had anything to do with magic?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:02.19,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one in this world who's not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.38,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,As long as one has desire, that alone makes them a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.54,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,So you already knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.82,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it wasn't my intention to hurt that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.73,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But this time it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.42,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:20.92,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.97,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, you weren't the target I was aiming for.{I'm sorry, you weren't the target I was trying to hurt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.91,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are lots of strange kids in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.41,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:38.62,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I just used the blue letters to remove the fire element that signifies regeneration and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:43.63,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's magic that disables those who are already hurt badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.53,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.33,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use if I don't destroy the card to stop this spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:58.01,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to save him, you have no choice but to beat big sis quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:01.32,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't know how much more can he endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.99,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that time is against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.71,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.95,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how valuable the Stab Sword is to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.34,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how that thing can change history,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.80,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,or how the world would change afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:24.46,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,But hurting others in order to obtain it is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.46,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a tool that only creates more pointless violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.96,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll destroy it with this hand of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:36.84,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I could say that I'm just doing a job, but that would disrespect my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:41.12,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The method for completion has been left in big sis' hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.11,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing with other people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.07,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.63,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.51,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,If she hits me with that spell from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.67,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The next one will be a shadow sword. {The next one will be a shadow blade.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.00,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I promise not to bore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.52,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't she using the attack from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:23.35,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Big sis has no interest in reusing the same spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.89,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.82,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is just foreplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.44,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,don't tell me you're out of strength already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.60,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.37,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,She did say that she wouldn't use the same spell twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.36,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,But she has so many combinations...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.42,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Next is "Blade Crater."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.85,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.69,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you move from that spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.80,Index II main I,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die if I move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.75,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:33.93,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,All the effort Fukiyose put into making the Daihaseisai a success, is going to waste because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.84,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,And you think I'll just stand still and let you do your thing? {You thought I could leave it like this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:43.57,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be able to placate me, Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.40,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You... idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.33,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To think his right hand had that much strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.59,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.39,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.31,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.37,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.86,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What a violent boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.80,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look, my button came off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:13.53,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was a pretty good punch, for an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:19.07,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But, big sis is accustomed to fighting strong opponents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.86,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Someone at your level leaves me feeling unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:33.00,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll leave that thing in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.21,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean our game has ended yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.47,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be turning up the heat from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.05,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.07,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.20,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That spell only lasts 20 minutes. It'll wear off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.70,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You worrywart Esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.30,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.91,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, destroy the Stab Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.33,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,With your right hand it should be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.35,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to destroy it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.35,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What if Academy City is attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:13.73,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be the one to take the blame if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.72,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,This is Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:20.32,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,For magicians, this place is the middle of enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:24.01,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,They'll calm down and plan a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.77,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.22,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:29.72,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,I'll discuss with my superiors about the next move we should take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.23,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.07,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.61,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.42,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.78,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:57.44,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I encountered some trouble, but I made it here just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.71,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.24,Index II main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:06.40,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave everything to big sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.35,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:14.12,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Since they've gotten the billboard, they probably already know about the Stab Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.80,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.97,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't affect the trade at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.19,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.28,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No one can get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:34.37,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Since this trade will bring happiness to everybody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.48,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The original Stab Sword does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:44.67,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The legends are just rumors that people passed around...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:52.38,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything written here true, Charles Conder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.99,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I am deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:58.13,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We at the British Museum only discovered this recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.51,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what exactly is that thing's heritage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.10,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:08.96,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Because the tales about it have snowballed over the years, we cannot be completely certain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.53,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.00,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.33,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They call it, "Croce di Pietro."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:22.04,Index II main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which should be translated as, "The tool used to crucify Peter."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.38,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Peter's Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:32.11,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning of this deal they're planning has completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:38.00,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If this trade is completed, Academy City will surely meet its end. {If this trade is completed, Academy City will collapse.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.75,Index II main I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, something much more terrible than that will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.00,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.58,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:54.18,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,"Croce di Pietro," translated as "Saint Peter's Cross."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.93,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,The Vatican, base of the Roman Catholic Church, was established on land bequeathed by Saint Peter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:04.63,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,by entombing his body in the ground and erecting a cross to mark the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.81,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,It also works in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.23,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,In reverse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:13.81,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Any place where the "Croce di Pietro" is erected will become the dominion of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.99,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,That includes Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:16.66,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Dominion? {Control?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:21.51,Index II main,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,It means that every action will benefit the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:25.76,Index II main,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,No one will recognize the change, as if it had always been that way from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:31.63,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how heavy the burdens or unfair the requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:35.04,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,This will become a place where people can only feel happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:35.59,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:41.72,Index II main,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,If Academy City falls under the dominion of the Roman Catholic Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:47.38,Index II main,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,This world, in which science and magic rest in a delicate balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.69,Index II main,Yellow,0000,0000,0000,,will tilt towards the Roman Catholics.{ will go over concentration the Roman Catholics.一極集中}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.29,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's the point of this trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:57.12,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's probably the right to dominate Academy City as well as rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.01,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop this trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:16.99,Index II main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, the world may face a reality far worse than destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.54,Index II main,Purple,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:30.19,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,A world where everyone can only feel happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.50,Index II main overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.73,Index II main overlap,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.76,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tou... ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:39.75,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't understand it well{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.62,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:48.59,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible, there's no way Index would wear clothes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.74,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.62,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you look me in the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.07,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.35,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:06.61,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:11.34,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought about some weird scene, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:16.98,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can see happiness written all over Touma's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.32,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.29,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what happened to your usual clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.56,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I left them with Komoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.93,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.87,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:32.75,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,You are hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:39.42,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be meeting with my parents for lunch soon, so please be patient until then{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.54,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.58,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.74,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.56,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:53.25,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to cheer for Touma, so I put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.45,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But where did you run off to on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.33,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:02.83,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my hardest so I could spend time with Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:09.35,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed to do when you just disappear like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:14.82,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. I thought you were just angry because you were hungry like usual{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.74,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.66,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:19.63,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm angry because you're not paying attention to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:25.66,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how can you say I'm mad like usual because I'm hungry? That's not Sister-like at all, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.71,Index II main overlap,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Index, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.46,Index II main overlap,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why aren't you biting like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.54,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, you don't have to force yourself{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.66,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Touma's so perverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:39.15,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who's always biting {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.18,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is perverted is you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.72,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:50.01,Index II main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's been hours since we last saw Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.87,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just look at the number of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.98,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It might take a while to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.47,Index II main,Wman2,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! So we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.51,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this morning, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.88,Index II main,WM2,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you for your help back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.26,Index II main,WM2,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you that I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.40,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they? Friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:20.85,Index II main,WM2,0000,0000,0000,,They're the parents of that boy you're so interested in, Mikoto-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.98,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, we are the Kamijous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:25.87,Index II main,WM,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.73,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,T-Th-Th-That's{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.56,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, appeal, appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.16,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like that! What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.27,Index II main overlap,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, have you had lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.46,Index II main,Wm,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.51,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, how about eating with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.05,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,I know a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.95,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? We'd be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.51,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:54.37,Index II main,Blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry, I'm just not used to crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.57,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I wasn't paying attention either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.97,Index II main,Blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.92,Index II main,Wm,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! What could this mean, Touya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:07.43,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, Okaa-san, you're mistaken! {It's not that, Mother, you're mistaken!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.97,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to stare, it was just so sudden that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.29,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.53,Index II main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like father, like son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.82,Index II main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.28,Index II main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.10,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.35,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's all thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.01,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.51,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.05,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.95,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:43.78,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that I always get zero results when I'm with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:47.51,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I was sorta just going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.35,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.67,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,As if {\i1}you'd{\i0} have any sort of flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.24,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this girl who follows you around all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:58.07,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,where does she live and who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.15,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.54,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.22,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.83,Index II main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,She came along with you when we went to the seaside{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.77,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Seaside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:13.21,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,You two went to the seaside together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.08,Index II main,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that Short Hair over there? Where does {\i1}she{\i0} live?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.70,Index II main,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,Is she Touma's girlfriend or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.57,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:26.05,Index II main,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,You came to cheer for Touma's school, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.24,Index II main,Blue,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I saw you at the Wrench Stick{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.35,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.30,Index II main,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,You, just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:34.67,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.01,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we eat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:40.39,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you are Kamijou Touma-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.53,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.83,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Are you Misaka's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:46.22,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:50.44,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,I am Misaka Misuzu, Mikoto's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.24,Index II main,Wm2,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.54,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:30.55,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,By solving the hidden puzzles, we move one step at a time towards understanding their goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:33.61,Index II main,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,But something happens to Himegami when we run into her on accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.94,Index II main,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode: Stab Sword"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:39.22,Index II main,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, the story begins.
